# English Only

All project artifacts must be written exclusively in English:

- Folder and file names (kebab-case or PascalCase)
- Variable, function, type, and prop names
- Comments and documentation
- UI copy, labels, placeholders, error messages, and aria-labels
- URL routes
- Skill files in `skills/`

Do not introduce Spanish or other non-English text in the codebase.
